      "seed": 2095443554,
      "version": 1376,
      "versionNonce": 2053107510,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784044643942,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Dropbox\n\nFunctional Requirements -> Core Entities -> API -> High Level Design -> Deep Dives\n\nFunctional Requirements:\n1. User should be able to upload an object.\n2. User should be able to download an object.\n3. Automatically sync objects across devices for each user.\n\nNon-Functional Requirements:\n1. Availability >> Consistency\n    Its more for the objects to be avaialble across devices even if they are not the most updated version\n         - Eventually Consistent\n2. Low latency in downloads and uploads\n3. Support large files up to 50 GB and the ability to resume from the point of failure\n4. High data integrity. Sync should be accurate across different devices.\n\n\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Dropbox\n\nFunctional Requirements -> Core Entities -> API -> High Level Design -> Deep Dives\n\nFunctional Requirements:\n1. User should be able to upload an object.\n2. User should be able to download an object.\n3. Automatically sync objects across devices for each user.\n\nNon-Functional Requirements:\n1. Availability >> Consistency\n    Its more for the objects to be avaialble across devices even if they are not the most updated version\n         - Eventually Consistent\n2. Low latency in downloads and uploads\n3. Support large files up to 50 GB and the ability to resume from the point of failure\n4. High data integrity. Sync should be accurate across different devices.\n\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
