      "updated": 1784044206997,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "file-metadata\n- fileId\n- createtimestamp\n- latestUpdatetimestamp - Null for version 1\n- previoustimestamp - Nulll for version 1 (latestUpdatedtimestamp of previous version)\n- version\n- uuid\n- size\n- s3 presigned url\n- chunks [\n        {hashed chunk id, status, s3 presigned url, \n            createtimestamp, lastUpdatetimestamp, previousTimestamp}\n        {.......}\n        {.......}\n    ]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
