      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784043977368,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Low latency in downloads and uploads",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Low latency in downloads and uploads",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6ZBJowTo_4tvYqAhg_e9r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 283.6441938485127,
      "y": 1855.7892314650092,
      "width": 770.8595581054688,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3Q",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1708542582,
      "version": 821,
      "versionNonce": 160538666,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784044285957,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Support large files up to 50 GB and the ability to \nresume from the point of failure\n\nClient App must do\n- Chunking\n- Writing metadata of each chunk to the File Metadata DynamoDb\n- Hash each chunk to get unique chunk Id\n-  Get presigned url of each chunk \n- Upload each chunk to S3 using presigned url\n- Update the metadata of the status of each chunk\n    - This helps in identifying how much of the file is already uploaded and\nwhat to upload on retry\n- Download only the chunks which are changed\n- Stich the updated chunk to file",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Support large files up to 50 GB and the ability to \nresume from the point of failure\n\nClient App must do\n- Chunking\n- Writing metadata of each chunk to the File Metadata DynamoDb\n- Hash each chunk to get unique chunk Id\n-  Get presigned url of each chunk \n- Upload each chunk to S3 using presigned url\n- Update the metadata of the status of each chunk\n    - This helps in identifying how much of the file is already uploaded and what to upload on retry\n- Download only the chunks which are changed\n- Stich the updated chunk to file",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "b3dsl7gbTxHCBdUBXqWjO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 785.9794613632644,
      "y": 1872.549147713992,
      "width": 706.6394653320312,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3R",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1096957930,
      "version": 21,
      "versionNonce": 1285867882,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784043980024,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. High data integrity. Sync should be accurate across different devices.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. High data integrity. Sync should be accurate across different devices.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
